                <div class="flex-1 max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8"><span class="text-xs block">(Haptic)</span>
                        Feedback</h1>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xl" style="flex: 2">
                    Expose your product. Share your journey by finding early adopters and gathering valuable
                    feedback to make your final creation amazing.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article
                    class="mb-4 lg:mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start bg-white shadow-xl p-12 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl">
                <div class="flex-1 max-w-md">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-0 md:mr-8">Build your story</h1>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xl" style="flex: 2">
